  <summary date="2021-06-01T13:01:43Z" status="Introduced in House">Taxi Medallion Loan Forgiveness Debt Relief Act of 2021

This bill excludes from gross income, for income tax purposes, income of a taxpayer, other than a C corporation, attributable to the discharge of qualified taxi medallion indebtedness that is discharged before 2023.</summary>
